4Geeks Academy offers a course titled "Become a AI Machine Learning Engineer". This course is designed for individuals with no previous knowledge in the field and aims to help them start a career as a data scientist and build their first machine learning models. The course is 16 weeks long and includes 3 classes per week with a maximum class size of 12 people. Upon completion, students receive a recognized certificate. The course covers Python, SQL, Looker, Streamlit, and Statistics, and teaches students to create predictive models using libraries such as Pandas and Numpy. Students also learn about algorithms like Close Neighbors and Decision Trees, as well as supervised and unsupervised learning models. They practice solving real-life cases and develop their own AI projects. The course is available in both English and Spanish. For more information, visit the website: [https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning). stop